data.name: FP_TopLabel.Text
data.value: On this page you can install one of available and tested FPS-configs into selected game. Settings, obtained from FPS-config, have higher priority than set in Graphic Tweaker or by game itself. Select config to read it's description.

data.name: HD_WelcMsg.Text
data.value: On this page you can install one of available and tested by us HUDs into the game. Please do not install more than one HUD because it can lead to unpredictable consequences. Each HUD has readme file and screenshot. Select one from list and you will be able to see it.
